funkatronics.code.tactilewaves.com.android

Class BluetoothAndroid

  • java.lang.Object
    • funkatronics.code.tactilewaves.com.android.BluetoothAndroid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bluetooth

    public class BluetoothAndroid
extends java.lang.Object
implements Bluetooth
    Class for Bluetooth Serial Communication (Standard Serial COM over Bluetooth) Accepting connections and managing connections are handled in separate threads to prevent any blocking of the main thread. State information is passed to the main activity for UI updates.
